ST MARGARETS FAIR 2018 DONATIONS
----------------------------------------------------------------------

    The St Margarets Fair is always an annual highlight for the local
    community. There was a great line-up of music and entertainment,
    stalls run by local businesses and organisations, the dog show, a
    breath-taking display by the Castellers of London and Barcelona,
    and even a big screen for those who wanted to watch England play
    Sweden in the World Cup.

